
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Fremont vs Mathog — Position Swap Analysis</title>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f0f2f5; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 13px; }

  .page-header { background: #1f4e78; color: #fff; padding: 16px 28px 12px; }
  .page-header h1 { font-size: 19px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .page-header .sub { font-size: 12px; color: #a8c4e0; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .badge { background: #2e75b6; color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 11px; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 3px; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .badge.green { background: #2d4a1e; }
  .editable-note { color: #7ec8f0; font-weight: 600; }
  .reset-btn { background: none; border: 1px solid #5b8ab5; color: #a8c4e0; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 3px; cursor: pointer; }
  .reset-btn:hover { background: #2e75b6; }
  #save-status { font-size: 11px; color: #7ec8f0; font-weight: 600; }

  .wrapper { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 18px 16px 40px; }
  .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .grid-4 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px; }

  .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.10); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .card-header { background: #1f4e78; color: #fff; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 7px 14px; }
  .card-header.green  { background: #2d4a1e; }
  .card-header.teal   { background: #1d6b6b; }
  .card-header.amber  { background: #7a5500; }
  .card-header.purple { background: #4a1e6e; }
  .card-header.slate  { background: #374151; }
  .card-body { padding: 12px 14px; }

  .sub-header { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .07em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #1f4e78; border-bottom: 1px solid #d0dcea; padding-bottom: 4px; margin: 10px 0 7px; }
  .sub-header:first-child { margin-top: 0; }

  .row { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 3px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; min-height: 28px; }
  .row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .row label { color: #444; flex: 1; padding-right: 10px; }
  .row .val { min-width: 120px; text-align: right; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a; }
  .row .val.dash { color: #aaa; font-weight: 400; }
  .row .val.neg  { color: #c00; }
  .row .val.pos  { color: #2d7a2d; }

  input[type=text], input[type=date] {
    border: none; border-bottom: 1.5px solid #2563eb; color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: transparent;
    text-align: right; width: 120px; outline: none; padding: 2px 4px;
  }
  input[type=text]:focus, input[type=date]:focus { background: #eff6ff; border-radius: 2px 2px 0 0; }

  /* Waterfall mini */
  .wf-mini { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0; margin: 3px 0; }
  .wf-num { width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%; background: #1f4e78; color: #fff; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .wf-num.green { background: #2d4a1e; }
  .wf-label { flex: 1; padding: 0 8px; font-size: 12px; color: #333; }
  .wf-amt { min-width: 100px; text-align: right; font-weight: 700; color: #1f4e78; font-size: 12px; }

  /* Swap table */
  .swap-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; }
  .swap-table thead th { background: #d9e1f2; color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: 700; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; padding: 7px 10px; text-align: right; border-bottom: 2px solid #b0bfe0; }
  .swap-table thead th:first-child { text-align: left; }
  .swap-table tbody tr { border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
  .swap-table tbody td { padding: 7px 10px; vertical-align: middle; text-align: right; }
  .swap-table tbody td:first-child { text-align: left; font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px; }
  .swap-table tfoot td { background: #fff2cc; font-weight: 700; padding: 7px 10px; border-top: 2px solid #e0c040; text-align: right; }
  .swap-table tfoot td:first-child { text-align: left; }
  .pos-label { font-size: 11px; color: #555; font-weight: 400; display: block; }
  .deal-tag { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .06em; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .deal-tag.fremont { background: #d9e1f2; color: #1f4e78; }
  .deal-tag.mathog  { background: #d5f0e8; color: #1d6b6b; }

  /* Delta cards */
  .delta-card { background: #fff; border-radius: 6px; box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.10); padding: 14px; text-align: center; }
  .delta-card .party-name { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .delta-card .gives-gets { font-size: 11px; color: #666; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .delta-card .delta-val { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; }
  .delta-card .delta-val.pos { color: #2d7a2d; }
  .delta-card .delta-val.neg { color: #c00; }
  .delta-card .delta-val.zero { color: #888; }
  .delta-card .delta-label { font-size: 10px; color: #888; margin-top: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; }
  .delta-card .pos-arrow { font-size: 11px; margin-top: 8px; }

  .notes { font-size: 12px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
  .notes p { margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .how-it-works { font-size: 11px; color: #777; line-height: 1.6; padding: 10px 0 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin-top: 10px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="page-header">
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:6px;">
    <span class="badge green">FREMONT</span>
    <span style="color:#a8c4e0;">×</span>
    <span class="badge" style="background:#1d6b6b;">MATHOG</span>
    <h1>Position Swap Analysis</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="sub">
    <span>As of Date: <input type="date" id="analysisDate" oninput="save('analysisDate');calc()" style="color:#fff;border-bottom-color:#7ec8f0;width:140px;"></span>
    <span class="editable-note">blue = editable</span>
    <button class="reset-btn" onclick="resetDefaults()">Reset Defaults</button>
    <button class="reset-btn" id="file-save-btn" onclick="enableFileSave()">📁 Enable File Auto-Save</button>
    <span id="save-status"></span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrapper">

  <!-- ═══ Deal Inputs ═══ -->
  <div class="grid-2">

    <!-- Mathog Inputs -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header teal">Mathog — Deal Inputs</div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="sub-header">Dates</div>
        <div class="row"><label>Pref Start Date</label><input type="date" id="mathogPrefStart" oninput="save('mathogPrefStart');calc()"></div>

        <div class="sub-header">Tenant Rent Roll &amp; Valuation</div>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto auto auto;gap:0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#444;padding:3px 0 4px;border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0;">
          <span>Tenant</span><span style="text-align:right;min-width:90px;">NNN Rent</span><span style="text-align:right;min-width:70px;">Cap Rate</span><span style="text-align:right;min-width:90px;">Value</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <label>Tenant 1</label>
          <input type="text" id="t1Rent" oninput="save('t1Rent');calc()" style="width:85px;">
          <input type="text" id="t1Cap" oninput="save('t1Cap');calc()" style="width:60px;">
          <span class="val dash" id="t1Val">—</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <label>Tenant 2</label>
          <input type="text" id="t2Rent" oninput="save('t2Rent');calc()" style="width:85px;">
          <input type="text" id="t2Cap" oninput="save('t2Cap');calc()" style="width:60px;">
          <span class="val dash" id="t2Val">—</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <label>Tenant 3</label>
          <input type="text" id="t3Rent" oninput="save('t3Rent');calc()" style="width:85px;">
          <input type="text" id="t3Cap" oninput="save('t3Cap');calc()" style="width:60px;">
          <span class="val dash" id="t3Val">—</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row" style="background:#f8f9fa;font-weight:700;">
          <label>Total Property Value</label><span class="val dash" id="mathogPropVal">—</span>
        </div>

        <div class="sub-header">Sale Costs &amp; Debt</div>
        <div class="row"><label>Cost of Sale %</label><input type="text" id="mathogCostPct" oninput="save('mathogCostPct');calc()"></div>
        <div class="row"><label>Tenant Improvements</label><input type="text" id="mathogTI" oninput="save('mathogTI');calc()"></div>
        <div class="row"><label>Leasing Commissions</label><input type="text" id="mathogLC" oninput="save('mathogLC');calc()"></div>
        <div class="row"><label>Bank Debt Payoff</label><input type="text" id="mathogDebt" oninput="save('mathogDebt');calc()"></div>
        <div class="row" style="background:#f8f9fa;font-weight:700;border-top:2px solid #d9e1f2;">
          <label>Net Equity Available</label><span class="val dash" id="mathogNetEq">—</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Fremont Inputs -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">Fremont — Deal Inputs</div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="sub-header">Dates</div>
        <div class="row"><label>Pref Start Date</label><input type="date" id="fremontPrefStart" oninput="save('fremontPrefStart');calc()"></div>
        <div class="row"><label>GR2 Pref Start Date</label><input type="date" id="gr2PrefStart" oninput="save('gr2PrefStart');calc()"></div>

        <div class="sub-header">Valuation</div>
        <div class="row"><label>Property Value</label><input type="text" id="fremontPropVal" oninput="save('fremontPropVal');calc()"></div>

        <div class="sub-header">Sale Costs &amp; Debt</div>
        <div class="row"><label>Cost of Sale %</label><input type="text" id="fremontCostPct" oninput="save('fremontCostPct');calc()"></div>
        <div class="row"><label>Tenant Improvements</label><input type="text" id="fremontTI" oninput="save('fremontTI');calc()"></div>
        <div class="row"><label>Leasing Commissions</label><input type="text" id="fremontLC" oninput="save('fremontLC');calc()"></div>
        <div class="row"><label>Bank Debt Payoff</label><input type="text" id="fremontDebt" oninput="save('fremontDebt');calc()"></div>
        <div class="row" style="background:#f8f9fa;font-weight:700;border-top:2px solid #d9e1f2;">
          <label>Net Equity Available</label><span class="val dash" id="fremontNetEq">—</span>
        </div>

        <div class="sub-header">Equity Stack</div>
        <div class="row"><label>GR — Pref Equity</label><input type="text" id="grPrefEq" oninput="save('grPrefEq');calc()"></div>
        <div class="row"><label>GR — Pref Rate</label><input type="text" id="grPrefRate" oninput="save('grPrefRate');calc()"></div>
        <div class="row"><label>GR2 — Pref Equity</label><input type="text" id="gr2PrefEq" oninput="save('gr2PrefEq');calc()"></div>
        <div class="row"><label>GR2 — Pref Rate</label><input type="text" id="gr2PrefRate" oninput="save('gr2PrefRate');calc()"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ Current Distributions ═══ -->
  <div class="grid-2">

    <!-- Mathog waterfall -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header teal">Mathog — Current Distributions</div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:#888;margin-bottom:8px;">
          Accrued: <strong id="mathogYears">—</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Net Equity: <strong id="mathogNetEq2">—</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="wf-mini"><div class="wf-num">1</div><div class="wf-label">GR (Outside Investor) — Accrued Pref</div><div class="wf-amt" id="m_t1">—</div></div>
        <div class="wf-mini"><div class="wf-num">2</div><div class="wf-label">GR — Return of Capital</div><div class="wf-amt" id="m_t2">—</div></div>
        <div class="wf-mini"><div class="wf-num">3</div><div class="wf-label">RS &amp; RG — Accrued Prefs</div><div class="wf-amt" id="m_t3">—</div></div>
        <div class="wf-mini"><div class="wf-num">4</div><div class="wf-label">RS &amp; RG — Return of Pref Capital</div><div class="wf-amt" id="m_t4">—</div></div>
        <div class="wf-mini"><div class="wf-num">5</div><div class="wf-label">Common Equity — Pro-rata (JB / RS / RG)</div><div class="wf-amt" id="m_t5">—</div></div>
        <div class="wf-mini"><div class="wf-num green">6</div><div class="wf-label" style="color:#2d4a1e;font-weight:700;">Residual — Split ÷ 3 (JB / RS / RG)</div><div class="wf-amt" style="color:#2d4a1e;" id="m_t6">—</div></div>
        <div style="border-top:1px solid #eee;margin-top:8px;padding-top:8px;">
          <div class="row"><label style="font-weight:700;color:#1d6b6b;">GR total (OI)</label><span class="val dash" id="m_gr_tot">—</span></div>
          <div class="row"><label style="font-weight:700;">JB total (P1)</label><span class="val dash" id="m_jb_tot">—</span></div>
          <div class="row"><label style="font-weight:700;">RS total (P2)</label><span class="val dash" id="m_rs_tot">—</span></div>
          <div class="row"><label style="font-weight:700;">RG total (P3)</label><span class="val dash" id="m_rg_tot">—</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Fremont waterfall -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">Fremont — Current Distributions</div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:#888;margin-bottom:8px;">
          Accrued (GR): <strong id="fremontYears">—</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Net Equity: <strong id="fremontNetEq2">—</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="wf-mini"><div class="wf-num">1</div><div class="wf-label">GR — Accrued Pref</div><div class="wf-amt" id="f_t1">—</div></div>
        <div class="wf-mini"><div class="wf-num">2</div><div class="wf-label">GR — Return of Capital</div><div class="wf-amt" id="f_t2">—</div></div>
        <div class="wf-mini"><div class="wf-num" style="background:#2d7a2d;">3</div><div class="wf-label">GR2 — Accrued Pref</div><div class="wf-amt" id="f_t3">—</div></div>
        <div class="wf-mini"><div class="wf-num" style="background:#2d7a2d;">4</div><div class="wf-label">GR2 — Return of Capital</div><div class="wf-amt" id="f_t4">—</div></div>
        <div class="wf-mini"><div class="wf-num">5–7</div><div class="wf-label">Partner prefs / common equity</div><div class="wf-amt" id="f_t57">—</div></div>
        <div class="wf-mini"><div class="wf-num green">8</div><div class="wf-label" style="color:#2d4a1e;font-weight:700;">Residual — Split ÷ 3 (JB / RS / RG)</div><div class="wf-amt" style="color:#2d4a1e;" id="f_t8">—</div></div>
        <div style="border-top:1px solid #eee;margin-top:8px;padding-top:8px;">
          <div class="row"><label style="font-weight:700;">GR total (pref)</label><span class="val dash" id="f_gr_tot">—</span></div>
          <div class="row"><label style="font-weight:700;">GR2 total</label><span class="val dash" id="f_gr2_tot">—</span></div>
          <div class="row"><label style="font-weight:700;">JB total (residual)</label><span class="val dash" id="f_jb_tot">—</span></div>
          <div class="row"><label style="font-weight:700;">RS total (residual)</label><span class="val dash" id="f_rs_tot">—</span></div>
          <div class="row"><label style="font-weight:700;">RG total (residual)</label><span class="val dash" id="f_rg_tot">—</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ Position Swap Comparison ═══ -->
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header purple">Position Swap Comparison — As of <span id="hdr_date">—</span></div>
    <div class="card-body" style="padding:0;">
      <table class="swap-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Party</th>
            <th>Current Position</th>
            <th>Current Value</th>
            <th>Swapped Position</th>
            <th>Swapped Value</th>
            <th>Cash Delta</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>JB</td>
            <td><span class="deal-tag mathog">Mathog</span><br><span class="pos-label">Partner 1 — Common equity ($485k), pro-rata common &amp; residual ÷3</span></td>
            <td id="sw_jb_cur">—</td>
            <td><span class="deal-tag fremont">Fremont</span><br><span class="pos-label">GR's position — $500k pref @10%, priority tiers 1–2</span></td>
            <td id="sw_jb_new">—</td>
            <td id="sw_jb_delta" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;">—</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>RS</td>
            <td><span class="deal-tag mathog">Mathog</span><br><span class="pos-label">Partner 2 — $275k pref @10%, common equity ($485k)</span></td>
            <td id="sw_rs_cur">—</td>
            <td><span class="deal-tag fremont">Fremont</span><br><span class="pos-label">RG's position — 1/3 of Fremont residual (tier 8)</span></td>
            <td id="sw_rs_new">—</td>
            <td id="sw_rs_delta" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;">—</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>GR</td>
            <td><span class="deal-tag fremont">Fremont</span><br><span class="pos-label">$500k pref @10%, priority tiers 1–2</span></td>
            <td id="sw_gr_cur">—</td>
            <td><span class="deal-tag mathog">Mathog</span><br><span class="pos-label">JB's position — Common equity ($485k), pro-rata common &amp; residual ÷3</span></td>
            <td id="sw_gr_new">—</td>
            <td id="sw_gr_delta" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;">—</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>RG</td>
            <td><span class="deal-tag fremont">Fremont</span><br><span class="pos-label">1/3 of Fremont residual (tier 8)</span></td>
            <td id="sw_rg_cur">—</td>
            <td><span class="deal-tag mathog">Mathog</span><br><span class="pos-label">RS's position — $275k pref @10%, common equity ($485k)</span></td>
            <td id="sw_rg_new">—</td>
            <td id="sw_rg_delta" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;">—</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <div class="how-it-works" style="padding:10px 14px 14px;">
      <strong>Swap logic:</strong> JB gives up Mathog Partner 1 → receives GR's Fremont pref position.
      RS gives up Mathog Partner 2 → receives RG's 1/3 Fremont residual.
      GR gives up Fremont pref → receives JB's Mathog P1.
      RG gives up Fremont residual → receives RS's Mathog P2.
      Cash Delta = Swapped Value − Current Value. Positive = better off, negative = worse off.
      Note: other positions each party holds (e.g. JB's own Fremont residual, GR's Mathog OI position) are unchanged and not shown here.
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ Delta Cards ═══ -->
  <div class="grid-4">
    <div class="delta-card">
      <div class="party-name">JB</div>
      <div class="gives-gets">Gives up: Mathog P1<br>Receives: GR's Fremont pref</div>
      <div class="delta-val" id="dc_jb_delta">—</div>
      <div class="delta-label" id="dc_jb_label">—</div>
      <div class="pos-arrow" id="dc_jb_arrow"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="delta-card">
      <div class="party-name">RS</div>
      <div class="gives-gets">Gives up: Mathog P2<br>Receives: RG's Fremont residual</div>
      <div class="delta-val" id="dc_rs_delta">—</div>
      <div class="delta-label" id="dc_rs_label">—</div>
      <div class="pos-arrow" id="dc_rs_arrow"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="delta-card">
      <div class="party-name">GR</div>
      <div class="gives-gets">Gives up: Fremont pref<br>Receives: JB's Mathog P1</div>
      <div class="delta-val" id="dc_gr_delta">—</div>
      <div class="delta-label" id="dc_gr_label">—</div>
      <div class="pos-arrow" id="dc_gr_arrow"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="delta-card">
      <div class="party-name">RG</div>
      <div class="gives-gets">Gives up: Fremont residual<br>Receives: RS's Mathog P2</div>
      <div class="delta-val" id="dc_rg_delta">—</div>
      <div class="delta-label" id="dc_rg_label">—</div>
      <div class="pos-arrow" id="dc_rg_arrow"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ Cash Equalization ═══ -->
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header" style="background:#5a3e8a;">Cash Equalization — What Each Party Pays to Make the Swap Fair</div>
    <div class="card-body" style="padding:0;">
      <table class="swap-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Swap Pair</th>
            <th>Better-Off Party</th>
            <th>Worse-Off Party</th>
            <th>Advantage</th>
            <th>Equalization Payment</th>
            <th>Direction</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td style="font-weight:700;">JB ↔ GR</td>
            <td id="eq_jbgr_winner">—</td>
            <td id="eq_jbgr_loser">—</td>
            <td id="eq_jbgr_adv">—</td>
            <td id="eq_jbgr_pay" style="font-weight:700;font-size:14px;">—</td>
            <td id="eq_jbgr_dir" style="font-size:12px;color:#555;">—</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="font-weight:700;">RS ↔ RG</td>
            <td id="eq_rsrg_winner">—</td>
            <td id="eq_rsrg_loser">—</td>
            <td id="eq_rsrg_adv">—</td>
